item.title: UA TEST3 Flip the pickle over. I'm sorry Summer, your opinion means very little to me. I'm Mr. Crowbar, and here is my friend, who is also a crowbar!
item.description: UA TEST 3 How do you saddle a fart? What is this, 90’s Conan? If it were, you could call ME Ernest Hemingway. Nothing to read into there! Why are you doing this bit? We’re gonna die. Shadow Jacker, you haven’t come out of your masturbation cave in eons! I wish that shotgun was my penis.
